!! Paul's Point
Paul's point as he lays his hand on him, "Timothy, the faith that first dwell in your mother and your grandmother is the same faith. The holy Spirit that dwells in you is also dwelling in me."

What you see that in the faith of others, is it not the same spirit?

What is Timothy without Paul? He is Paul.

